  <h4>Design checks</h4>
  <p class="ref">
   [EN 1992-1-1, § 9.2.1.1]
   <p>Minimum tensile reinforcement ratio</p>
   <p>
    <span class="eq">
     <var>ρ</var>
     <sub>min</sub>
     =
     <b>max</b>
     <span class="b1">(</span>
     <span class="dvc">
      0.26 ·
      <var>f</var>
      <sub>ctm</sub>
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      <var>f</var>
      <sub>yk</sub>
     </span>
     ; 0.0013
     <span class="b1">)</span>
     =
     <b>max</b>
     <span class="b1">(</span>
     <span class="dvc">
      0.26 · 2.21
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      500
     </span>
     ; 0.0013
     <span class="b1">)</span>
     = 0.0013
    </span>
   </p>
   <p>
    Maximum tensile reinforcement ratio -
    <span class="eq">
     <var>ρ</var>
     <sub>max</sub>
     = 0.04
    </span>
   </p>
   <p>
    Internal section forces as a function of the compressive zone depth
    <i>x</i>
    .
   </p>
   <p>Reinforcement strain:</p>
   <p>
    - in bottom reinforcement -
    <span class="eq">
     <var>ε</var>
     <sub>s1</sub>
     (
     <var>x</var>
     )  =
     <span class="dvc">
      <var>ε</var>
      <sub>cu2</sub>
      ·  (
      <var>d</var>
      −
      <var>x</var>
      )
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      <var>x</var>
     </span>
    </span>
   </p>
   <p>
    - in top reinforcement -
    <span class="eq">
     <var>ε</var>
     <sub>s2</sub>
     (
     <var>x</var>
     )  =
     <span class="dvc">
      <var>ε</var>
      <sub>cu2</sub>
      ·  (
      <var>d</var>
      <sub>2</sub>
      −
      <var>x</var>
      )
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      <var>x</var>
     </span>
    </span>
   </p>
   <p>
    - at flange bottom edge -
    <span class="eq">
     <var>ε</var>
     <sub>cf</sub>
     (
     <var>x</var>
     )  =
     <span class="dvc">
      <var>ε</var>
      <sub>cu2</sub>
      ·  (
      <var>x</var>
      −
      <var>h</var>
      <sub>f</sub>
      )
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      <var>x</var>
     </span>
    </span>
   </p>
   <p>Factors for integration of concrete stress diagram</p>
   <p>
    <span class="eq">
     <var>k</var>
     =
     <var>f</var>
     <sub>cd</sub>
     ·
     <var>ε</var>
     <sub>cu2</sub>
     = 11.33 · 0.0035 = 0.0397
    </span>
   </p>
   <p>
    <span class="eq">
     <var>k</var>
