     +
     <var>z</var>
     <sub>0</sub>
     = 650 − 147.5 + 86.93 = 589.43
    </span>
    mm
   </p>
   <p>Bending moment capacity</p>
   <p>
    <span class="eq">
     <var>M</var>
     <sub>Rd</sub>
     =  (
