     <sub>s</sub>
     (
     <var>ε</var>
     <sub>s1</sub>
     ( 147.5 )  )  ·  ( 589.43 − 50 )  + 0 ·
     <var>σ</var>
     <sub>s</sub>
     (
     <var>ε</var>
     <sub>s2</sub>
     ( 147.5 )  )  ·  ( 589.43 − 650 + 50 )  )  · 10
     <sup>-6</sup>
     = 867.77
    </span>
    kN·m
   </p>
   <p>Design bending moment is lower than bending capacity:</p>
